data.description: Looking for that country home on over one acre with mature trees?  You've found it!! Check out this 2600sf 3/2.5 home w/oversized 3 car attached garage, detached 20 x 20 work shop with electric, front covered porch w/built in gazebo, gutters, on a corner lot w/ separate fenced area makes a great play area for the children or an FFA project.  This one has 2 HVAC systems, 2 water heaters, fireplace in living room, office/study, breakfast area and formal dining off kitchen, lots of counter space, granite counter tops w/ custom cabinets.  It's a MUST SEE!
